{"tid":1399642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[將軍澳遊行] 將軍澳好多藍絲","createTime":"2019-08-03T08:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T16:19:54.000Z","uid":270181,"like":77,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"f9853389052ec30254555b4312269c9d90816c15","tid":1399642,"uid":270181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:39:23.000Z","msg":"大家唔好只係記得港島西。<br />\n仲有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將軍澳遊行</span></span>！<br />\n如題將軍澳好多藍絲，因為都幾多中產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以人多可以保護手足，<br />\n大家唔好覺得遠而放棄唔入將軍澳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將軍澳需要各位呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n完咗將軍澳之後一齊轉場去<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">港島西</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一齊尼一齊走，保護各位手足<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">明天將軍澳見</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aedbf16efa858a61004c409904f08a609b9506a","tid":1399642,"uid":270181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832a1dfc7532ca2b86a30406e60cd7321e1024c0","tid":1399642,"uid":270181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48f6834bc38ba1543b6a75a0f9e18911c8a8c17","tid":1399642,"uid":64938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:44:48.000Z","msg":"[香城online]傳令兵的技巧和心得<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382782</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n就快